质，但是只要是清醒的人都明白其中的边缘性，你要是跟我用智障正确来争论，用什么啊普通人也有大智慧，边缘人也有大作为这种揣着明白装糊涂的观点来杠，我不理你，有魅力这个描述要是看不懂，就想想那个角色你会不会去追他和他喜结连理。"},"attached_info":"Cj4I1+vD/vTSxUAQAxoINzAzMDIxOTYgjvDuiQYwADjpC0AJcgk0ODYwOTI4Mjl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"86 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-7e5407d3ad8e08a49d61bbced61d35dc_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"10_1743651351.162207","card_id":"Q_1888685528414660511","target":{"id":1888685528414660600,"title":"黄金价格会不会迎来暴跌？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1888685528414660511","type":"question","created":1743077720,"answer_count":154,"follower_count":423,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1346,26559],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"2025年以来，金价的价格一路飙升上涨，再接下来会不会迎来一次大跌？"},"attached_info":"CkkI1+vD/vTSxUAQAxoJMTE0MjAzNzYwINiClb8GMAA4pwNACnITMTg4ODY4NTUyODQxNDY2MDUxMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"85 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-30e1274542bb5540f711f7c47edf1995_1440w.webp"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1743651351.163599","card_id":"Q_1888599018352894736","target":{"id":1888599018352894700,"title":"用你现在的英语水平翻译这句话「He is a zero」，该怎么翻译？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1888599018352894736","type":"question","created":1743057094,"answer_count":407,"follower_count":448,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[165,20678],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkkI1+vD/vTSxUAQAxoJMTE0MTk3ODE3IMbhk78GMAA4wANAC3ITMTg4ODU5OTAxODM1Mjg5NDczNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"83 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"c